dct_title_s: Honduras city graphic 1:12,500. Tegucigalpa. Series E952.
dct_description_sm: Map shows major buildings, churches, schools, roads, trails, and populated areas. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Includes indexes of numbered features, glossary, location map, and boundaries map. "Reprinted by NIMA 4-00." "Feature revisions are portrayed in magenta." "NIMA ref. no. E952XTEGUCIGA." "NSN 7643014018690." This is a map of the city of Tegucigalpa, Honduras, shown at a 1:12,500 scale. The map was created for use by Department of Defense by the Defense Mapping Agency.
dct_creator_sm: United States. Defense Mapping Agency. Hydrographic/Topographic Center
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic-Topographic Center, 1984.
Bethesda, M.D. : National Imagery and Mapping Agency, 2000.
